translations: v．越冬：指动植物在冬季生存下来，进入春季。
· The plant overwinters as a dormant bulb.
这种植物以休眠的球茎形式度过冬季。

sentences.sentence: It has three generations a year in Shanghai and overwinters asa diapaused larva in the head of the garlic and the dead cotton boll.
sentences.translation: 在上海一年发生三代，以滞育幼虫在蒜头和枯棉铃组织内越冬。
